rows.label: qst003103_msg0001
rows.name:
What? Are you here to
help with distribution?

rows.label: qst003103_msg0002
rows.name: I see. That's a big help.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0003
rows.name:
This distribution center is
short on dishes made with meat.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0004
rows.name:
It'd be a great help if you
could make some meat dishes
and bring them here.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0005
rows.name:
Thanks for your help. Looks
like we'll manage now.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0006
rows.name:
We've been busy ever since the
Acedian refugees arrived.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0007
rows.name:
To be honest, I'd like
to kick them out.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0008
rows.name:
We can't even provide enough
for our own Invidian people...

rows.label: qst003103_msg0009
rows.name:
If we have to distribute to Acedian
refugees as well, it will be hard
to suppress the complaints.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0010
rows.name:
In fact, we've had frequent
trouble with the refugees lately.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0011
rows.name:
I do sympathize with the refugees
after what happened to them, but...

rows.label: qst003103_msg0012
rows.name:
They'll probably end up settling
here, so I'd like to eliminate
as much friction as possible.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0013
rows.name:
Anyway, thanks. You've given
us some breathing room.

rows.label: qst003103_msg0014
rows.name:
What this distribution
center needs is meat dishes.
I'm counting on you.
